venue.name: Pawtuckaway Lake Fundy Cove Launch

item.description:
A few of us are planning to kayak on Pawtuckaway Lake today meeting at the Fundy Cove Boat Launch at noon.

Directions: Take Rt. 156 to Deerfield Rd. Nottingham NH. Look for Boat Ramp sign on right then turn onto road on left across from sign. The address in the link below is an approximation.

http://maps.google.co...

Due to the very cold water temps a wet suit or dry suit is necessary to be safe on the water this time of year. Also the temps will only reach the mid 30s and there will be a breeze so dress warm and bring extra clothing.

Today... Sunny. Highs in the mid 30s. Northeast winds around 10 mph this morning...Becoming light and variable.
item.name: Early Season Paddle on Pawtuckaway Lake from Fundy Cove Boat Launch
